headline: UBS Maintains Buy Rating On Bunge (BG) On Biofuel Prospects
summary: Bunge Global SA (NYSE:BG), founded in 1818 and based in Missouri, is a global agribusiness and food company. Its main segments are Agribusiness, Refined and Specialty Oils, Milling, and Sugar and Bioenergy. It ranks 7th on our list of the S&P 500 stocks with a low PE ratio.
